%N A394711 Decimal expansion of the asymptotic probability that two positive integers selected independently at random are coprime and both are nonsquarefree numbers.
%F A394711 Equals 6/Pi^2 - 2 * Product_{p prime} (1 - 2/p^2 + 1/p^3) + Product_{p prime} (1 - 3/p^2 + 2/p^3) = A059956 - 2 * A065464 + A065473.
%F A394711 Equals A229099^2 * A394712.
